* Sends bulk email results after the race is finalized.
*   When to use:    After all errors are fixed and "Event to Database" has been run.
*   How to use:     Double-click to email results to all runners with an EMAIL and TIME.
*   Setup:          Configure SendGrid API key and sender in Entries.INI (%email_apikey%, %email_from%).
*   Note:           Ensure "Event to Database" is run first to populate result fields.

/* Before running: You MUST execute the "Event to Database" command.
This copies Finish Times and Places into the participant records so
this script can find them.
*/

Header

Your results for the %full name% race:

.End of Header
Destination         temp.txt
Records Per Page    1
Page Length         3
From Page Number    1
To Page Number      1000
No Column Headers
No Page Numbers
No Total

Select              EMAIL
NE
And
Select              TIME
NE

* Message Construction
Field               Name
Message             : Time:
Space               1
Field               TIME
Message             . Div:
Space               1
Field               DIVPLACE
Message             /
Field               DIVTOTAL
Message             . Full Results:
Space               1
Field               Result URL

EMAIL TO            EMAIL
Email Subject       %email_subject% - Your Results
EMAIL SERVER        sendgrid
EMAIL APIKEY        %email_apikey%
EMAIL FROM          %email_from%
